message.rftoolsbuilder.builder:
@fThis block can quarry areas, pump liquids,
@fmove/copy/swap structures, collect items
@fand XP, move entities, build structures, ...
@eInfusing bonus: reduced power consumption
@eand increased speed.

message.rftoolsbuilder.composer:
@fThis block can construct more complex
@fshape cards for the Builder or Shield
@fby creating combinations of other shape
@fcards

message.rftoolsbuilder.locator:
@fPlace this block on top of a Scanner
@fto extend its functionality with the ability
@fto locate entities and machines using power

message.rftoolsbuilder.scanner:
@2Scan id: %s
@fThis block can scan an area and link
@fto shape cards for the Builder or Shield.
@fThe resulting shape card can also be used
@fin the Composer

message.rftoolsbuilder.remote_scanner:
@2Scan id: %s
@fThis block can scan an area and link
@fto shape cards for the Builder or Shield.
@fThe resulting shape card can also be used
@fin the Composer
@6This version can scan scan through a
@6dialed matter transmitter which should be
@6located above it
